title: Vixen - Abigail Mac (Lets Get Physical: Part 2) NEW 03 June 2017
description: After Abigail's fun at her last shoot, she is in constant demand and is now moving to LA permanently. With a fabulous new photographer on the job, she knows that she will do well. All she has to do is go the extra mile to leave a lasting impression on him. After the photoshoot has finished, she offers a repayment for the excellent opportunity he has given her. Needless to say, he knows exactly what's on the menu.  ​​​​​​​ http://img.imgdone.com/image/zZQZ http://img.imgdone.com/image/zOAJ
